#CSC500 - Mod1 CT - Part1 - Psuedocode
#Desc - Psuedocode - Add and subtract numbers and display equations
#Jeff Roggen

#inputsection
    input "Enter first number" into num1 #input 1
    display "The first number is:" + num1
    input "enter second number" into num2 #input 2
    display "Second number is:" + num2

#processing section
    sum num1 and num2 and display the equation
    subtract num2 from num1 and display the equation

#output section
    display num1 + num2 "=" total
    display num1 - num2 "=" difference

#end
